353
00:32:41,770 --> 00:32:45,910
♪Farewell, the happiness that isn't mine to have♪

354
00:32:46,140 --> 00:32:50,410
♪Let's pray time can erase my memory♪

355
00:32:50,650 --> 00:32:52,680
